            </div>

            {/* Enhanced Statistics */}
            <div className="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-4">
              <h3 className="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">üìä ‡∏™‡∏ñ‡∏¥‡∏ï‡∏¥ Smart AI</h3>
              <div className="space-y-2">
                <div className="flex justify-between">
                  <span className="text-gray-400">‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏°‡∏±‡πà‡∏ô‡πÉ‡∏à‡∏õ‡∏±‡∏à‡∏à‡∏∏‡∏ö‡∏±‡∏ô:</span>
