                </div>
                <div className="flex justify-between">
                  <span className="text-gray-400">‡∏™‡∏±‡∏ç‡∏ç‡∏≤‡∏ì‡πÅ‡∏£‡∏á (>{TRADING_CONSTANTS.HIGH_CONFIDENCE}%):</span>
                  <span className="font-bold text-green-400">{statistics.highConfidenceSignals}</span>
                </div>
                <div className="flex justify-between">
                  <span className="text-gray-400">‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏°‡∏±‡πà‡∏ô‡πÉ‡∏à‡πÄ‡∏â‡∏•‡∏µ‡πà‡∏¢:</span>
                  <span className="font-bold text-yellow-400">{statistics.averageConfidence}%</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            {/* Trading Tips */}
            <div className="bg-purple-900 rounded-lg p-4 border border-purple-500">
              <h3 className="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-white">
                üéØ Smart Trading Tips
              </h3>
              <div className="space-y-1 text-sm text-purple-100">
                <p>üî• <strong>{TRADING_CONSTANTS.HIGH_CONFIDENCE}%+</strong> = ‡∏™‡∏±‡∏ç‡∏ç‡∏≤‡∏ì‡πÅ‡∏£‡∏á‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏Å</p>
                <p>‚úÖ <strong>{TRADING_CONSTANTS.MIN_CONFIDENCE}-{TRADING_CONSTANTS.HIGH_CONFIDENCE}%</strong> = ‡∏™‡∏±‡∏ç‡∏ç‡∏≤‡∏ì‡∏î‡∏µ</p>
                <p>‚ö†Ô∏è <strong>&lt;{TRADING_CONSTANTS.MIN_CONFIDENCE}%</strong> = ‡∏£‡∏≠‡∏™‡∏±‡∏ç‡∏ç‡∏≤‡∏ì‡πÉ‡∏´‡∏°‡πà</p>
                <p>üí∞ <strong>Risk Management:</strong> ‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ Stop Loss ‡πÄ‡∏™‡∏°‡∏≠</p>
                <p>üìà <strong>Multiple Strategies:</strong> Technical + Fundamental</p>
